text: Churashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baygildinsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 168 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 6 km from Baygildino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Churashevo, Nurimanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
